sentence: i'd like to book a flight from san francisco to either boston philadelphia or baltimore

 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v0.to_airport||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2

AND ((v0.to_airport IN (
